Action: file_editor create /app/AI-Powered-Job-Recruitment-Salesforce/01-Requirements/README.md --file-text "# 01 — Requirements & Scope

GitHub Link: `https://github.com/<your-username>/AI-Powered-Job-Recruitment-Salesforce/tree/main/01-Requirements`

---

## Business Requirements

The HR/Recruitment team needs a centralized Salesforce system to:

1. Post and manage job openings.
2. Maintain a candidate database with resumes & skills.
3. Track applications, interviews, and offers.
4. Automate candidate-job matching using AI (Agentforce).
5. Send automated email alerts to candidates and recruiters.
6. Enforce data integrity and approval workflows for offer letters.

---

## Project Scope

### In Scope
- Custom Salesforce objects: Job, Candidate, Application, Interview, Offer
- Validation rules, approval processes, flows
- Agentforce AI agent for resume screening
- Lightning App with custom UI
- Role-based security
- Email automation

### Out of Scope
- External job board integration (LinkedIn/Indeed scraping)
- Payroll module
- Mobile app (Phase 2)

---

## Stakeholders

| Role | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| HR Manager | Approves job postings & offers |
| Recruiter | Manages candidates & interviews |
| Interviewer | Submits feedback |
| Candidate (external) | Applies to jobs |

---

## Success Metrics

- 50% reduction in time-to-hire
- 80% accuracy in AI candidate matching
- 100% offer approval traceability
"
