Action: file_editor create /app/AI-Powered-Job-Recruitment-Salesforce/02-Objects/README.md --file-text "# 02 — Objects Creation

GitHub Link: `https://github.com/<your-username>/AI-Powered-Job-Recruitment-Salesforce/tree/main/02-Objects`

---

## Custom Objects

### 1. Job__c
**Label:** Job  
**Plural:** Jobs  
**Record Name:** Job Number (Auto Number, `JOB-{0000}`)

### 2. Candidate__c
**Label:** Candidate  
**Plural:** Candidates  
**Record Name:** Candidate Name (Text)

### 3. Application__c
**Label:** Application  
**Plural:** Applications  
**Record Name:** Application Number (Auto Number, `APP-{0000}`)

### 4. Interview__c
**Label:** Interview  
**Plural:** Interviews  
**Record Name:** Interview Number (Auto Number, `INT-{0000}`)

### 5. Offer__c
**Label:** Offer  
**Plural:** Offers  
**Record Name:** Offer Number (Auto Number, `OFF-{0000}`)

---

## Metadata XML

### Job__c.object-meta.xml
```xml
<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>
<CustomObject xmlns=\"http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata\">
    <label>Job</label>
    <pluralLabel>Jobs</pluralLabel>
    <nameField>
        <displayFormat>JOB-{0000}</displayFormat>
        <label>Job Number</label>
        <type>AutoNumber</type>
    </nameField>
    <deploymentStatus>Deployed</deploymentStatus>
    <sharingModel>ReadWrite</sharingModel>
    <enableActivities>true</enableActivities>
    <enableReports>true</enableReports>
    <enableSearch>true</enableSearch>
</CustomObject>
```

